locations.title: Picking Up The Pieces
locations.description:
**Mission Giver:** Shani  
**Location:** Dam Battlegrounds, The Spaceport, Buried City

**Objectives:**
- Visit any area on your map with a loot category icon.
- Loot 3 containers

**Granted Items:**
- Binoculars

**Rewards:**
- Kettle II Assault Rifle
- Light Ammo x100

locations.description:

**Mission Giver:** Shani  

**Objectives:**
- Obtain 6 Wires
- Obtain 1 Battery

**Rewards:**
- Tactical Mk. 1 Augment
- Adrenaline Shots x3

- Destroy 3 ARC enemies

locations.description:
